DiabloCalc.skilltips||(DiabloCalc.skilltips={}),DiabloCalc.passivetips||(DiabloCalc.passivetips={}),DiabloCalc.skilltips.demonhunter={bolas:{a:'<p>Increase the explosion radius to <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Shoot <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> bolas that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Cold. The bolas no longer explode for area damage to nearby enemies.</p><p>Enemies hit have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to be <span class="d3-color-green">Frozen</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',d:'<p>When the bola explodes, you have a <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> chance to gain <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Discipline.</p><p>Bolas\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Augment the bola to deal <span class="d3-color-green">216%</span> weapon damage as Fire to the enemy and <span class="d3-color-green">148%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards, but increases the explosion delay to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"lit",d:"lit",e:"fir",x:"fir"},icon:1573036684,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1573036684\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot out an explosive bola that wraps itself around the enemy. After <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second, the bola explodes dealing <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to the enemy and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">110%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all other enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},caltrops:{a:'<p>Enemies in the area also take <span class="d3-color-green">270%</span> weapon damage as Physical over <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the slowing amount to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p>',c:'<p>When the trap is sprung, all enemies in the area are immobilized for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost of Caltrops to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Become empowered while standing in the area of effect, gaining an additional <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span> Critical Hit Chance.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:810901144,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/810901144\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Discipline</p><p>Lay a trap of caltrops on the ground that activates when an enemy approaches. Once sprung, the caltrops Slow the movement of enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yards by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>. This trap lasts <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>4</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},chakram:{a:'<p>A second Chakram mirrors the first. Each Chakram deals <span class="d3-color-green">220%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The Chakram path turns into a loop, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">400%</span> weapon damage as Lightning to enemies along its path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The Chakram follows a slow curve, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Cold to enemies along the path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The Chakram spirals out from the targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along the path.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Surround yourself with a cloud of spinning Chakrams, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage per second as Physical to nearby enemies. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> minutes.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>57</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1799143751,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1799143751\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a swirling Chakram that deals <span class="d3-color-green">380%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along its path.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>12</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},clusterarrow:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of the explosion at the impact location to <span class="d3-color-green">850%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Instead of releasing grenades, release up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">600%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Launch a cluster through the air, dropping grenades in a straight line that each explode for <span class="d3-color-green">650%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Instead of releasing grenades, release up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">450%</span> weapon damage as Cold. You gain <span class="d3-color-green">2%</span> Life per enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by the grenades have a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to be stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p><p>Cluster Arrow\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:324597533,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/324597533\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">40</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a cluster arrow that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">650%</span> weapon damage as Fire into a series of <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> additional grenades that each explode for <span class="d3-color-green">250%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},companion:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your spider throws webs at all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards of you and him, Slowing them by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a spider companion that attacks enemies in front of him for <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The spider\'s attacks Slow enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your boar charges to you, then taunts all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a boar companion that attacks enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The boar increases your and your party\'s Life regeneration by <span class="d3-color-green">10728</span> and resistance to all elements by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>41</em>.</p>',c:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your wolf howls, granting you and your allies within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> increased damage for <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a wolf companion that attacks enemies in front of him for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',d:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Instantly gain <span class="d3-color-green">50</span> Hatred.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a bat companion that attacks for <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The bat grants you <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Hatred per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Instantly pick up all health globes and gold within <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> yards.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a pair of ferret companions that each attack for <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p><p>The ferrets collect gold for you, increase gold found on monsters by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>, and increase your movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:439848148,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/439848148\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Active:</span> Your raven deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> damage on its next attack.</p><p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Summons a raven companion that pecks at enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of your weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},elementalarrow:{a:'<p>Shoot a frost arrow that hits an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> weapon damage as Cold then splits into up to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> additional frost arrows. Enemies hit are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Shoot a ball of lightning that electrocutes enemies along its path for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Shoot a fiery arrow that hits an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire and explodes, immolating the ground for <span class="d3-color-green">315%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Shoot a shadow tentacle that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Physical to enemies along its path and returns <span class="d3-color-green">0.4%</span> of your maximum Life for each enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Shoot an electrified bolt for <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Lightning that Stuns enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second on a Critical Hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>43</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:184977554,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/184977554\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot a fire arrow that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies it passes through.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},entanglingshot:{a:'<p>Increase the Slow duration to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds.</p><p>Entangling Shot\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Entangle and Slow up to <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> enemies with each shot.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Entangled enemies take <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>18</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Entangling Shot\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Increase the Slow amount to <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"lit",d:"fir",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1589427902,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1589427902\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Imbue an arrow with shadow energy that deals <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage to the primary enemy and entangles up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> enemies, slowing their movement by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>When Entangling Shot hits an enemy, the Slow effect on all entangled enemies is refreshed.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>3</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},evasivefire:{a:'<p>Instead of backflipping, your Armor is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the damage of side bolts to <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>34</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Whenever a backflip is triggered, leave a bomb behind that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage as Physical in a <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> yard radius after <span class="d3-color-green">0.6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the backflip distance to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yards.</p><p>Evasive Fire\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Instead of backflipping, increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Evasive Fire\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"fir",c:"phy",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:2594005641,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2594005641\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot a spread of bolts that hits the primary enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage and two additional enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> weapon damage.</p><p>If an enemy is in front of you at close range, you will backflip away <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> yards.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},fanofknives:{a:'<p>Remove the cooldown but add a <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Hatred cost.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Also throw long-range knives that deal <span class="d3-color-green">620%</span> weapon damage to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> additional enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Enemies hit are Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds and increase damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1600%</span> weapon damage as Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> additional armor for <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p><p>Fan of Knives\' damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:1221625994,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1221625994\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> seconds</p><p>Throw knives out in a spiral around you, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">620%</span> weapon damage to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards. Your knives will also Slow the movement of enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},grenade:{a:'<p>Throw a grenade that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Cold and leaves a cloud that deals an additional <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds to enemies who stand in the area and <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> them.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Throw cluster grenades that deal <span class="d3-color-green">200%</span> weapon damage as Fire over a <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> yard radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Throw out <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire each.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Hurl a Lightning grenade that has a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to Stun enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"fir",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:1383355833,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1383355833\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Throw a grenade that bounces and explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">160%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},hungeringarrow:{a:'<p>Increase Hatred generated to <span class="d3-color-green">7</span>.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p>',b:'<p>If the arrow successfully pierces the first enemy, the arrow splits into <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> arrows.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Each consecutive pierce increases the damage of the arrow by <span class="d3-color-green">70%</span>.</p><p>Hungering Arrow\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>42</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Increase the chance for the arrow to pierce to <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>6</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits cause a burst of bone to explode from the enemy, dealing <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"col",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1893827298,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1893827298\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Generate:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a magically imbued arrow that seeks out enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">155%</span> weapon damage and has a <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> chance to pierce through them.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Primary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>1</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},impale:{a:'<p>The knife <span class="d3-color-green">pierces</span> through all enemies in a straight line for Cold damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The impact causes Knockback and has a <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> chance to Stun for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>7</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The enemy also burns for <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>15</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The knife ricochets to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> additional nearby enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards of each other.</p><p>Impale\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>53</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Critical Hits deal <span class="d3-color-green">330%</span> additional damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2594944828,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2594944828\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred</p><p>Throw a knife that impales an enemy for <span class="d3-color-green">750%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>2</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},markedfordeath:{a:'<p><span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> of damage dealt to the marked enemy is also divided evenly among all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>When the enemy is killed, the mark spreads to the closest <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards. This effect can chain repeatedly.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Mark an area on the ground of <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> yard radius for <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds. Enemies in the area take <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Attacks you make against the marked enemy generate <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>48</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Attackers heal for up to <span class="d3-color-green">3%</span> of their maximum Life when damaging the marked enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:746746961,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/746746961\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline</p><p>Mark an enemy. The marked enemy takes <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> additional damage for the next <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},multishot:{a:'<p>Increase the damage of Multishot to <span class="d3-color-green">500%</span> weapon damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Enemies hit are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> and have <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased chance to be Critically Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>31</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Every time you fire, launch <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> rockets at nearby enemies that each deal <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the Hatred cost to <span class="d3-color-green">18</span>.</p><p>Multishot\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>26</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Knockback the first <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> enemies hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:303982585,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/303982585\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> Hatred</p><p>Fire a massive volley of arrows dealing <span class="d3-color-green">360%</span> weapon damage to all enemies in the area.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>22</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},preparation:{a:'<p>Restore <span class="d3-color-green">75</span> Hatred.</p><p>Preparation has a <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p>',b:'<p><span class="d3-color-gold">Passive:</span> Permanently increase maximum Discipline by <span class="d3-color-green">20</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> Discipline over <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> seconds instead of restoring it immediately.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> Life when using Preparation.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',e:'<p>There is a <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> chance that Preparation\'s cooldown will not be triggered.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3714052661,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3714052661\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">45</span> seconds</p><p>Instantly restore <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rainofvengeance:{a:'<p>Fire a massive volley of arrows at a large area. Arrows fall from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">2800%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to all enemies in the area.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Launch a volley of guided arrows that rain down on enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3500%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Summon a Shadow Beast that drops grenades from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">5800%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>54</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Call a group of <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Shadow Beasts to plummet from the sky at a targeted location dealing <span class="d3-color-green">3800%</span> total weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds and <span class="d3-color-green">Freezing</span> enemies hit for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Summon a wave of <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Shadow Beasts to tear across the ground, knocking back enemies and dealing <span class="d3-color-green">4600%</span> total weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>47</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"lit",b:"phy",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"fir",x:"phy"},icon:3422491597,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3422491597\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds</p><p>Fire a massive volley of arrows at a large area. Arrows fall from the sky dealing <span class="d3-color-green">1500%</span> weapon damage over <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds to all enemies in the area.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},rapidfire:{a:'<p>Rapidly fire grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">545%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within a <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yard radius.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Fire lightning arrows that have a <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> chance to pierce through enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While channeling Rapid Fire, launch <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> homing rockets every second. Each rocket deals <span class="d3-color-green">145%</span> weapon damage as Physical to nearby enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>32</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the initial Hatred cost to <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> and ignite your arrows, causing them to deal Fire damage.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>11</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies hit by Rapid Fire are <span class="d3-color-green">Chilled</span> by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p><p>Rapid Fire\'s damage turns into Cold.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"lit",c:"phy",d:"fir",e:"col",x:"phy"},icon:890686438,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/890686438\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred initially, and an additional <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> Hatred while channeling</p><p>Rapidly fire for <span class="d3-color-green">685%</span> weapon damage as Physical.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Secondary</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>5</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},sentry:{a:'<p>Create a chain between you and the Sentry and between each Sentry that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage every second to each enemy it touches.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p>',b:'<p>The turret now fires piercing bolts.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>36</em>.</p>',c:'<p>The turret will also fire homing rockets at random nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>28</em>.</p>',d:'<p>The turret <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> all nearby enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">16</span> yards, Slowing their movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>52</em>.</p>',e:'<p>The turret also creates a shield that reduces damage taken by allies by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"col",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:3326150325,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3326150325\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> Hatred</p><p>Summon a turret that fires at nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">280%</span> weapon damage. Lasts <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> seconds.</p><p>You may have <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> turrets active at a time.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">You gain a charge every <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> seconds and can have up to <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> charges stored at a time.</span></p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},shadowpower:{a:'<p>Slow the movement speed of enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> yards by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>21</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">30%</span> increased movement speed while Shadow Power is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>58</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Reduce damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">35%</span> while Shadow Power is active.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>51</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Double the total amount of Life per Hit gained.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1595292131,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1595292131\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> Discipline</p><p>Draw in the power of the shadows, gaining <span class="d3-color-green">26821</span> Life per Hit for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p><p>Life per Hit gained is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> of your Life per Kill.</p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},smokescreen:{a:'<p>Remove the Discipline cost but increase the cooldown to <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>59</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase the duration to <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">15%</span> Life while invisible.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Reduce the cost to <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>44</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> movement speed while invisible.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>14</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:498378287,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/498378287\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">14</span> Discipline<br/><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds</p><p>Vanish behind a wall of smoke, becoming momentarily invisible for <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second.</p><p><span class="d3-color-yellow">This ability does not start its cooldown until after its effects expire.</span></p> <p class="special">Defensive</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>8</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},spiketrap:{a:'<p>Increases damage to <span class="d3-color-green">1930%</span> weapon damage.</p><p>When deployed, enemies within range are instantly immobilized for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>39</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Increase to <span class="d3-color-green">2020%</span> weapon damage as Cold.</p><p>On detonation, the blast slows any targets hit for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Increase to <span class="d3-color-green">1900%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p><p>Hatred generators will now detonate traps.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Simultaneously lay <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> traps.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p>',e:'<p>When triggered lightning chain hits up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards.</p><p>Lightning will also arc from any triggered trap to any armed traps within <span class="d3-color-green">25</span> yards.<br/>All enemies are hit for <span class="d3-color-green">6700%</span> weapon damage as Lightning over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>46</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"phy",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"fir",e:"lit",x:"fir"},icon:3714901347,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3714901347\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">15</span> Hatred</p><p>Lay a trap that remains dormant until another Hatred spender is used to detonate the trap. When detonated, the trap and all other traps will explode in a chain reaction for <span class="d3-color-green">1160%</span> weapon damage as Fire to all enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> yards of each trap.</p><p>You can have a maximum of <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Spike Traps active at one time.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>17</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},strafe:{a:'<p>Throw out bouncy grenades that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">460%</span> weapon damage as Fire to enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">9</span> yards.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>56</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Leave an icy trail in your wake that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Cold over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds and <span class="d3-color-green">Chills</span> enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>24</em>.</p>',c:'<p>In addition to regular shots, shoot off homing rockets for <span class="d3-color-green">130%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Movement speed increased to <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span> of normal running speed while strafing.</p><p>Strafe\'s damage turns into Lightning.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>29</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Throw out knives rather than arrows that deal an extra <span class="d3-color-green">140%</span> damage on Critical Hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>37</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"col",c:"fir",d:"lit",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:2184421717,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2184421717\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">12</span> Hatred</p><p>Shoot at random nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">675%</span> weapon damage while moving at <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> of normal movement speed.</p> <p>Requires <span class="value">Bow</span></p> <p class="special">Archery</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>19</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},vault:{a:'<p>Leave a trail of fire in your wake that deals <span class="d3-color-green">300%</span> weapon damage as Fire over <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>49</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Remove the Discipline cost but add an <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> second cooldown.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>38</em>.</p>',c:'<p>While Vaulting, shoot <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> arrows for <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> weapon damage at nearby enemies. These shots are guaranteed Critical Hits.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p>',d:'<p>After using Vault, your next Vault within <span class="d3-color-green">6</span> seconds has its Discipline cost reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>33</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Enemies you vault through are knocked away and Stunned for <span class="d3-color-green">1.5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>23</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"fir",b:"phy",c:"phy",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1765480092,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1765480092\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cost:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">8</span> Discipline</p><p>Tumble acrobatically <span class="d3-color-green">35</span> yards.</p> <p class="special">Hunting</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>9</em>.</p> </div> </div>'},vengeance:{a:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, summon allies from the shadows that attack for <span class="d3-color-green">120%</span> weapon damage as Cold and <span class="d3-color-green">Freeze</span> your enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>69</em>.</p>',b:'<p>Vengeance fills your heart, reducing all damage taken by <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>63</em>.</p>',c:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, launch <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> Grenades at random enemies outside melee range on every attack that explode for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage each as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>62</em>.</p>',d:'<p>Instead of Homing Rockets, the side guns are powered up into slower-firing cannons that deal <span class="d3-color-green">225%</span> weapon damage and heal you for <span class="d3-color-green">3.0%</span> of maximum Life per enemy hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>65</em>.</p>',e:'<p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> Hatred per second.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>67</em>.</p>',elements:{a:"col",b:"lit",c:"fir",d:"phy",e:"phy",x:"phy"},icon:1368351649,x:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-skill d3-icon-skill-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1368351649\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p><span class="d3-color-gold">Cooldown:</span> <span class="d3-color-green">90</span> seconds</p><p>Turn into the physical embodiment of Vengeance for <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> seconds.</p><p><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Side Guns:</span> Gain <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> additional piercing shots for <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> weapon damage each on every attack.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Homing Rockets:</span> Shoot <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> rockets at nearby enemies for <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> weapon damage each on every attack.<br/><span class="tooltip-icon-bullet"></span> <span class="d3-color-gold">Vengeance:</span> Gain <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> increased damage.</p> <p class="special">Devices</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>61</em>.</p> </div> </div>'}},DiabloCalc.passivetips.demonhunter={ambush:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/608154598\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>You deal <span class="d3-color-green">40%</span> additional damage to enemies above <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> health.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>64</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The art of surprise is difficult, but rewarding to master." —Mynton, Demon Hunter</div> </div>',archery:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3333952724\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain a bonus based on your weapon type:<br/>Bow: <span class="d3-color-green">8%</span> increased damage<br/>Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> Critical Hit Damage<br/>Hand Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">5%</span> Critical Hit Chance<br/>2nd Hand Crossbow: <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> Hatred per Second</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Feel the weight of the crossbow in your hand. Now... the wind, the distance, the target\'s speed. Good. Now try it with blood in your eyes and a demon at your throat." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',awareness:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3727829327\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>When you receive fatal damage, you instead vanish for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds and regenerate <span class="d3-color-green">50%</span> of maximum Life.</p><p>This effect may occur once every <span class="d3-color-green">60</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>66</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Everything is a test. Study your surroundings well, and you will pass." —Josen, Master Hunter</div> </div>',ballistics:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2724217296\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase damage of rockets by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>.</p><p>In addition, you have a <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> chance to fire a homing rocket for <span class="d3-color-green">150%</span> weapon damage when you attack.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>55</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"How should I know who first invented these devices? Just make sure the correct end is pointed at the enemy and they\'ll do the rest." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',bloodvengeance:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/671040338\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your maximum Hatred is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">25</span>. In addition, gain <span class="d3-color-green">30</span> Hatred and <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> Discipline when you are healed by a health globe.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>13</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"If it bleeds you can kill it. Kill this one slowly." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',brooding:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1860876243\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">3.0%</span> Life regeneration per second for every second you remain stationary, stacking up to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> times. This bonus is reset <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds after you move.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>25</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Never forget where you came from.</div> </div>',culltheweak:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4214899055\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase damage against Slowed or Chilled enemies by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"I\'ll show you the same mercy you showed my helpless family." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',customengineering:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3309907294\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the duration of your Caltrops, Marked for Death, Spike Trap, and Sentry by <span class="d3-color-green">100%</span>.</p><p>Increase the maximum number and charges of Sentries to <span class="d3-color-green">3</span> and number of Spike Traps to <span class="d3-color-green">5</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>40</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">The self-loading mechanisms built into most hand crossbows and traps are delicate and difficult to maintain. Extensive practice is required to use them properly.</div> </div>',grenadier:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2447865967\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase the damage of grenades by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.<br/>Increase the explosion size of grenades by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p><p>Upon death, you drop a giant grenade that explodes for <span class="d3-color-green">1000%</span> weapon damage as Fire.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>45</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Do not construct these devices by candlelight, nor by firelight. Once armed, be no closer than ten paces upon the count of three." —Explicit instructions from Quang the Chemist</div> </div>',hotpursuit:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/929589357\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Increase movement speed by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> seconds when you hit an enemy.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>27</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Don\'t make me chase you back to Hell, vermin. I know a quicker way to send you there." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',leech:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1324876423\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">18507</span> Life per Hit.</p><p>Heal amount is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">75%</span> of your Life per Kill.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>60</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"For a Demon Hunter, killing is life. Kill, grow strong, and survive." –Mynton, Demon Hunter\n</div> </div>',nightstalker:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/989292478\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Your primary skills generate an additional <span class="d3-color-green">4</span> Hatred.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>20</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"How did I learn to hate, to kill, to flay the flesh from the bones of my prey without pity? You taught me." —Tyla Shrikewing\'s final words to Naragh the Sin Eater</div> </div>',numbingtraps:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/3392294912\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies you Slow, Chill, or hit with Fan of Knives, Spike Trap, Caltrops, Grenades, and Sentry fire have their damage reduced by <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">5</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>30</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Demonic anatomy is strange and diverse. At times they defy sanity, but in other ways they are just as vulnerable as we are." —Meditations on the Enemy</div> </div>',perfectionist:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1477444155\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Reduce the Discipline cost of all skills by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>. Increase your Armor and resistance to all damage types by <span class="d3-color-green">10%</span>.</p><p>Discipline is used to fuel many of your tactical and defensive skills.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>35</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Once the trap is sprung you must not relent until every last enemy has fallen. To hesitate is to invite disaster.</div> </div>',sharpshooter:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/4022948488\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">4%</span> Critical Hit Chance every second. This bonus is reset <span class="d3-color-green">1</span> second after you successfully critically hit.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>50</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Every creature has a vulnerability. Find it, and put an arrow in it." —Greyscarr, Veteran Demon Hunter</div> </div>',singleout:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2280375200\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Gain <span class="d3-color-green">25%</span> Critical Hit Chance against enemies who are more than <span class="d3-color-green">20</span> yards away from any other enemies.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>68</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Wield your focus like a weapon.</div> </div>',steadyaim:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/2176454368\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>As long as there are no enemies within <span class="d3-color-green">10</span> yards, all damage is increased by <span class="d3-color-green">20%</span>.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>16</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"Flee if you can, demon. I have a quiver full of friends who fly faster than you." —Tyla Shrikewing</div> </div>',tacticaladvantage:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/852610358\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Whenever you use Vault, Shadow Power, Smoke Screen, or backflip with Evasive Fire you gain <span class="d3-color-green">60%</span> movement speed for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">Never start a fair fight.</div> </div>',thrillofthehunt:'<div class="tooltip-body "> <span class="d3-icon d3-icon-trait d3-icon-trait-64 " style="background-image: url(\'/webgl/icons/1178023747\'); width: 64px; height: 64px;"> <span class="frame"></span> </span> <div class="description"> <p>Enemies hit by your Hatred spenders are Slowed by <span class="d3-color-green">80%</span> for <span class="d3-color-green">2</span> seconds.</p> <p class="subtle">Unlocked at level <em>10</em>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="tooltip-extension "> <div class="flavor">"The first three were dead before they hit the ground. The others weren\'t so lucky." —Captain Rumford</div> </div>'};